 |above        = {{Flagu|French Guiana}}
 |subheader    = Prostitution illegal<br>Buying sex legal
}}
{{main|Prostitution in Overseas France#French Guiana}}
Although illegal, prostitution in [[French Guiana]] is common, especially in the gold mining areas of the interior.<ref name="fg">{{cite web|last1=Bellos|first1=Alex|last2=Oyapock|first2=River|title=Illegal, polluting and dangerous: the gold rush in French Guiana|url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2007/dec/17/pollution.mining|website=The Guardian|accessdate=27 December 2017|date=17 December 2007}}</ref> Some people are driven into prostitution by poverty.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fayet|first1=Rosane|title=Why are the people of French Guiana so angry?|url=https://www.equaltimes.org/why-are-the-people-of-french?lang=en#.WkP9Ed9l-M-|website=Equal Times|accessdate=27 December 2017|language=en|date=6 April 2017}}</ref> Thee [[HIV]] rate is the highest of any French territory, and sex workers are at risk due to inconsistent [[condom]] use.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Parriault|first1=Marie-Claire et all|title=Predictive factors of unprotected sex for female sex workers: first study in French Guiana, the French territory with the highest HIV prevalence|url=https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/f262/0154456dd74a23e04b8fde1ff7835a76885b.pdf|publisher=Centre d'Investigation Clinique Antilles Guyane|accessdate=27 December 2017}}</ref>
