{{main|Prostitution in Jamaica}}
Prostitution in [[Jamaica]] is illegal but widely tolerated,<ref name="indi">{{cite web|title=Women who travel for sex: Sun, sea and gigolos|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/women-who-travel-for-sex-sun-sea-and-gigolos-407202.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223010101/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home%2Dnews/women%2Dwho%2Dtravel%2Dfor%2Dsex%2Dsun%2Dsea%2Dand%2Dgigolos%2D407202.html|website=The Independent|accessdate=22 December 2017|archivedate=23 December 2008|dead-url=yes|date=9 July 2006}}</ref><ref name="inq"/> especially in tourist areas.<ref name="spl" />

