Prostitution is common on the [[Turks and Caicos Islands]], especially in [[Providenciales]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hamilton|first1=Deandrea S|title=Prostitution crack down necessary says Premier to Police Commish – Magnetic Media|url=http://magneticmediatv.com/2015/12/prostitution-crack-down-necessary-says-premier-to-police-commish/|website=Magnetic Media TV|accessdate=25 February 2018|date=23 December 2015}}</ref> Many of the sex workers are from Eastern Europe and the Dominican Republican.<ref name="eddys">{{cite web|title=Eddy's Place: Sex, sun and HIV|url=http://cousineddie.blogspot.co.uk/2006/10/sex-sun-and-hiv.html|website=Eddys Place|accessdate=25 February 2018|language=en|date=1 October 2006}}</ref> There is some [[female sex tourism]] on the islands.<ref name="eddys" /> [[Sex trafficking]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Rose|first1=Olivia|title=Stop sex trade - PDM|url=http://tcweeklynews.com/stop-sex-trade-pdm-p6934-149.htm|website=TC Weekly News|accessdate=25 February 2018|date=21 March 2016}}</ref> and [[HIV]]<ref name="eddys" /> are problems in the country.
